      "docs": "Usecase-layer mirror of domain CatalogueLinterRuleKind. Expanding from 3 unit variants to 12 variants in parallel with the domain type; NoPublicField remains unit while the other 11 variants carry rule parameters. Uses String fields for role / receiver / layer names instead of domain types (FieldName / RoleKind / SelfReceiver / LayerId) because the usecase boundary accepts external input from CLI/config before domain validation. The interactor converts LintRuleKind -> CatalogueLinterRuleKind during rule construction.",
