      "module_path": "catalogue_lint_workflow",
      "docs": "Concrete implementation of RunCatalogueLint. Modify from baseline: per D17, the evaluation logic moves from InMemoryCatalogueLinter (infrastructure) to domain::evaluate_catalogue_lint (pure function). The interactor no longer injects a CatalogueLinter evaluation port; it retains the CatalogueLoader port because loading CatalogueDocument from track_id/layer_id is external I/O. Generic over L: CatalogueLoader so callers pass concrete types without importing domain port traits directly (no Arc<dyn Trait> boxing at this boundary). The execute flow loads the requested catalogue and LayerId, converts LintRuleSpec into CatalogueLinterRule, then calls domain::evaluate_catalogue_lint directly.",
      "spec_refs": [
        {
          "file": "track/items/tddd-pattern-semantics-extension-2026-06-13/spec.json",
          "anchor": "IN-13"
        }
      ],
      "informal_grounds": []
