      "docs": "Errors from the RunCatalogueLint use case. Modify from baseline: CatalogueLoad continues to wrap CatalogueLoaderError because the interactor still performs external catalogue loading; LintExecution wraps domain CatalogueLinterError from evaluate_catalogue_lint rather than an infrastructure CatalogueLinter port. InvalidLayer(String) carries the unknown layer id; InvalidRuleSpec(String) carries the rejection reason from domain constructor validation.",
